{"tid":158745,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保良局訓練營涉虐待學生 黃大仙重案組接手調查","createTime":"2017-03-16T13:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T05:35:06.000Z","uid":54733,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"370f4b6036bf5c4cfe2d7a176102bcc40f2d8dfb","tid":158745,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489668690_2e56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489668690_2e56.jpg&h=d23b23c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保良局領袖紀律訓練營涉虐待學童事件，警方晚上回覆《蘋果》查詢時證實，昨日（3月15日）接獲一名男子報案，懷疑早前在一個訓練營內，有學員被不恰當對待，案件列作「求警調查」，現由黃大仙警區重案組第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n保良局領袖紀律訓練營連日爆出虐待學生醜聞，訓練營負責人、導航訓練中心總監盧錦昌今天接受《蘋果》專訪時亦承認，警方就近日爭議邀請中心職員協助調查，他們會全面配合。<br />\n<br />\n保良局昨晚深夜發表聲明，稱參與訓練營由屬校本決定，學校皆予正面評價，但強調不同意任何虐待、粗言或人身攻擊的行為，並已提醒訓練營加強提示導師，以學生利益為首。教育局表示，近年接獲數宗有關保良局領袖訓練營的查詢或投訴，已向相關學校提供意見及支援。<br />\n<br />\n被揭有學生參與訓練營期間涉受虐的基督書院表示，去年有個別中四級同學在奮進營舉行前，向校方表達一些有關外間訓練機構的意見及疑慮，惟經老師與同學及家長坦誠溝通，疑慮得以釋除，家長和同學都選擇參與，而在活動後的評估顯示，活動成效良佳。<br />\n<br />\n對於傳媒報道中，有教練在訓練過程命令學生「食草」，校方指，教師沒有見過，亦絕不認同這種手法，至今未有打算明年繼續聘用上述團隊，舉辦相類的訓練活動。校方又指，一直重視學生生命培育工作，關心學生身心成長，學校會透過正規或非正規課程培育學生，對學校主辦或委託外間機構主領的活動，均以學生的福祉為首要考慮，絕不容許任何危害學生身心安全的安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56437290&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56437290%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170316&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=231c7971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56437290%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170316&h=83e83685\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56437290&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170316</a>"},{"pid":"04a95903ef1ae38f50ea7a4325c37e570ca7c673","tid":158745,"uid":35460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7de50abf94542f1f827127ca3ab1e9b687364c1","tid":158745,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b460bb507ce23033b92617c573247c43fd09d52e","tid":158745,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dcc8def69ae863e2b2de5b94a264603b008fdd","tid":158745,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"虐待兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27af26b2b669c8fe05be4c8e9f7b906f88113cbf","tid":158745,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"王同學應該有好多證據係手"},{"pid":"eb3a907d790249cfa4e0b49a0f7d370dde3ee94b","tid":158745,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3da7863410f8e0bed358f20248e02a45d41048","tid":158745,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6f17b2befd1c4b0d3012622ac50c0359d76c4b","tid":158745,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc